Okay, Abrams.

03:36.925 --> 03:38.893
Allende.

03:40.470 --> 03:41.938
Bernstein.

03:45.142 --> 03:46.143
Brown.

03:49.771 --> 03:51.148
Come on, come on.

03:52.858 --> 03:54.280
Attboy, Todd

03:55.110 --> 03:56.202
Buckley.

04:01.992 --> 04:02.993
Cohen.

04:11.334 --> 04:12.460
Garcia.

04:19.718 --> 04:20.970
Paul.

04:29.853 --> 04:31.321
Take a seat, Lisa.

04:37.444 --> 04:40.448
