version of America

07:19.773 --> 07:21.821
that probably never
existed to begin with.

07:22.400 --> 07:24.573
Lisa has raised
a salient point.

07:28.323 --> 07:30.746
Tell him to be polite, tell
him to answer the questions,

07:30.825 --> 07:34.170
and I'll arrange for his bail
in the morning. Yes.

07:34.913 --> 07:36.915
Hey,
how'd you do?

07:36.998 --> 07:40.423
