or anything.

07:46.132 --> 07:47.930
He was totally
cool about it.

07:48.009 --> 07:49.477
He's so cool.

07:49.552 --> 07:51.930
Oh, yeah, everybody
loves Mr. Aaron.

07:52.222 --> 07:54.099
What's that supposed
to mean?

07:55.350 --> 07:57.728
Nothing. The man is
very lovable.

08:02.065 --> 08:03.612
What are you doing now?

08:03.817 --> 08:06.070
I was gonna go
look for a cowboy hat.

08:06.695 --> 08:07.821
Why?

08:08.196 --> 08:11.245
Because my dad is supposed to
take me and my brother

08:11.324 --> 08:13.577
to this ranch in New Mexico
to go horseback riding

08:13.660 --> 08:15.333
and I don't think
it would be right

08:15.453 --> 08:17.171
to appear on horseback
in New Mexico

08:17.247 --> 08:20.717
without the appropriate
equestrian paraphernalia, Darren.

08:20.792 --> 08:22.169
You wouldn't
understand these things.

08:22.252 --> 08:23.925
That is a
definite possibility.

08:24.087 --> 08:25.760
Anyway, thanks again.

08:25.880 --> 08:30.306
Well, before you venture forth on your
bizarre quest for a cowboy hat...

08:30.385 --> 08:31.932
Yes, Darren?

08:32.053 --> 08:33.600
