like on a date?

08:42.813 --> 08:47.240
No, not on a date,
just go to a movie.

08:47.902 --> 08:49.404
I don't know if
it's a fucking date!

08:49.487 --> 08:51.785
All right. Calm down.
What do you wanna see?

08:52.282 --> 08:55.126
I don't know, I don't
even know what's playing.

08:56.202 --> 08:58.125
I don't know
if it's a date.

08:59.080 --> 09:02.300
Let's just forget about it. I
hate the fucking' movies anyway.

09:02.375 --> 09:04.002
They're just bullshit.
They're all bullshit!

09:04.085 --> 09:06.804
Okay, take it easy. I'm sorry.
