a date, anyway?

09:13.636 --> 09:15.638
Would that be
so horrendous?

09:19.517 --> 09:22.316
Oh, my God.
Are you like...

09:23.229 --> 09:25.027
Are you asking me out?

09:29.736 --> 09:31.613
I don't know.
Are you?

09:31.696 --> 09:34.324
Yeah. I mean...

09:34.491 --> 09:36.084
I feel like we're
already really close...

09:36.159 --> 09:37.160
Oh, my God.

09:37.243 --> 09:39.666
...and I think we'd
be a really good match.

09:42.665 --> 09:46.715
Well, I would definitely
have to think about this.

09:46.795 --> 09:48.422
Absolutely.
Give it some thought.

09:48.505 --> 09:49.677
Okay. I will.

09:50.840 --> 09:51.841
Okay.

09:54.969 --> 09:56.186
Why do you look
like that?

09:56.304 --> 09:57.521
Like what?

09:58.556 --> 10:00.183
What do you want from me?
Not a thing!

10:00.850 --> 10:03.854
AH right. I'll see
you later.

10:04.437 --> 10:05.438
All right.

10:23.581 --> 10:24.628
Hello!

10:43.560 --> 10:44.732
Hi.

10:45.228 --> 10:46.275
Is Mom home?

10:46.396 --> 10:47.443
