10:52.986 --> 10:54.033
Hey!

10:54.112 --> 10:55.238
What are you
doing tonight?

10:55.405 --> 10:58.875
Nothing. Darren wants me
to go to the movies with him.

10:58.950 --> 11:01.373
Oh, my God.
What's that about?

11:01.703 --> 11:03.171
