to see you in that hat.

11:59.385 --> 12:01.808
Hey! Hey!

12:09.354 --> 12:10.651
Where'd you get...

12:10.813 --> 12:12.156
How you doin”?

12:12.690 --> 12:13.691
Your hat!

12:14.484 --> 12:15.485
What?

12:15.568 --> 12:17.161
