12:21.658 --> 12:23.035
What are you, crazy?

12:24.118 --> 12:25.119
Hi.

12:25.328 --> 12:27.501
Where'd you get
your cowboy hat?

12:28.206 --> 12:29.298
My hat?

12:29.415 --> 12:30.462
Yeah! Your cowboy hat!

12:30.541 --> 12:32.794
You like my cowboy hat?
Really?

12:33.419 --> 12:35.046
Yes! Where did you get it?

13:45.742 --> 13:46.914
Somebody see
what happen?

