14:01.591 --> 14:03.184
- You were in a bad accident.
- Who are you?

14:03.259 --> 14:04.681
My name is Lisa.

14:04.802 --> 14:06.224
What do you mean? Am I dead?

14:06.304 --> 14:07.681
No, you're not dead.

14:07.764 --> 14:09.516
You were in a traffic accident,
but you're gonna be...

14:09.599 --> 14:11.693
What do you mean?
What happened'?

14:11.768 --> 14:13.691
