14:22.945 --> 14:24.162
I think you're
a little confused.

14:24.280 --> 14:25.532
I'll say I'm confused.

14:25.615 --> 14:26.992
Here.
Let me just try...

14:27.075 --> 14:28.702
No! Don't let go!
Ma'am!

14:28.826 --> 14:31.955
- Don't let go of me! Don't let go of me.
- I won't.

14:32.038 --> 14:33.881
I won't. I'm not gonna let go.

14:33.956 --> 14:35.208
Thank you. Thank you, honey.

14:35.458 --> 14:37.256
She needs a tourniquet
or she's going to die.

14:37.335 --> 14:38.837
Okay, let me just...

14:38.920 --> 14:40.297
Oh, my God!

14:41.631 --> 14:42.632
Jesus Christ!

14:42.715 --> 14:45.810
Help! God, what's
happening to me!

14:47.387 --> 14:48.513
I'm sorry.

14:48.596 --> 14:50.564
I'm trying to put
a tourniquet on you.

14:50.640 --> 14:52.017
Ma'am, we need to get
a tourniquet on you.

14:52.100 --> 14:53.477
Do you have a belt?
You can use your belt.

14:53.559 --> 14:54.776
I just can't see
where to do it.

14:54.852 --> 14:56.149
You're gonna be
all right, so just hang on.

14:56.312 --> 14:58.440
Thank you, honey.
Just don't let go of me.

14:58.815 --> 15:00.237
They're gonna put
a tourniquet on you.

15:00.316 --> 15:02.694
What do you mean?
Are they doctors'?

15:02.777 --> 15:05.997
No, they're not doctors.
They were just passing by.

15:06.072 --> 15:07.073
Well, get 'em
the fuck away from me!

15:07.156 --> 15:08.123
Ma'am!

15:08.199 --> 15:10.247
Ma'am! We're only
trying to help you!

15:10.326 --> 15:12.044
Never mind that!
Just try putting it around...

15:12.120 --> 15:14.043
Do you wanna do it? You know how to do it.
You wanna do it?

15:14.122 --> 15:15.715
Are you kidding me!

15:15.790 --> 15:17.633
I can't see
anything.

15:19.168 --> 15:21.341
