15:32.098 --> 15:33.941
What do you mean?

15:34.183 --> 15:35.856
You were in
a terrible accident.

15:35.935 --> 15:38.438
But you're gonna be fine,
so just hang on, okay?

15:38.813 --> 15:42.317
There's no place to put it.
I can't even find a...

15:42.442 --> 15:44.285
Will somebody call
the fucking ambulance!

15:44.360 --> 15:45.953
Calm down!
We already called them!

15:46.028 --> 15:47.826
They're obviously
not coming fast enough,

15:47.947 --> 15:49.745
so maybe you
should call them again!

15:49.824 --> 15:51.201
