15:52.994 --> 15:54.371
You're gonna be...
Could somebody...

15:55.163 --> 15:56.836
Could somebody
call my daughter?

15:56.914 --> 15:59.087
Sure! We can call her.
What's her name?

16:00.376 --> 16:02.128
Just tell me her name
and give me her number.

16:02.211 --> 16:03.303
It's Lisa.

16:03.379 --> 16:05.723
No, that's my name.
Is that your daughter's name?

16:05.798 --> 16:07.971
What? What are you
talking about?

16:08.050 --> 16:10.098
I'm sorry. I'm not
trying to be confusing.

16:10.178 --> 16:12.180
My name is Lisa.
Is that your daughter's name?

16:12.263 --> 16:14.812
Jesus Christ, just call her!
Would you call her?

16:15.057 --> 16:18.027
I can't call her if you
don't give me the number.

16:18.269 --> 16:20.271
I got it.
I got it!

16:21.230 --> 16:22.447
Ma'am?

16:22.523 --> 16:24.150
- You're gonna be okay.
- You're gonna be okay!

16:24.233 --> 16:25.576
What's your
daughter's number?

16:26.152 --> 16:27.529
Sweetie,

16:29.405 --> 16:30.406
I don't think
I'm gonna make it.

16:30.490 --> 16:31.491
Oh, no!

16:31.574 --> 16:34.623
Please hang on. The ambulance
is gonna be here any minute!

16:34.702 --> 16:36.830
So just hang on, okay?

16:36.913 --> 16:38.085
Please!

16:38.247 --> 16:39.419
It's okay.

16:40.583 --> 16:41.835
She's gone.

16:41.959 --> 16:43.256
No! No!

16:43.961 --> 16:45.008
She's gone.

16:45.087 --> 16:46.054
Please let go of me!

16:46.130 --> 16:48.679
Please, let go of me!
Please, let go of me!

16:48.758 --> 16:51.978
Just hang on. They're gonna
be here any minute, okay?

16:52.053 --> 16:53.225
So just hang on!

16:53.638 --> 16:55.185
You're gonna be okay!

17:05.691 --> 17:06.692
You were going
the speed limit?

17:06.776 --> 17:07.777
Yeah.

17:08.069 --> 17:11.743
Lisa? You're Lisa? I just want to
ask you a few questions, okay?

17:11.821 --> 17:12.823
Yeah, sure.

17:12.906 --> 17:14.750
Now, just tell me
everything you saw,

17:14.825 --> 17:17.999
