not be important. All right?

17:18.079 --> 17:20.080
Think of it like a movie.
Like you're watching' a movie

17:20.164 --> 17:21.461
in your head...

17:21.582 --> 17:22.834
It was green as I
came to the intersection.

17:22.916 --> 17:23.884
Could
somebody call my mother?

17:23.960 --> 17:24.961
We already called
your mom,

17:25.044 --> 17:27.262
but I'll have 'em put another call
in to your mother right now, okay?

17:27.338 --> 17:28.760
I know this is
hard for you,

17:28.839 --> 17:31.217
but we gotta get this while it's
still fresh in your mind, okay?

17:31.300 --> 17:32.677
Some of these questions
might seem like

17:32.802 --> 17:34.224
