a lot of sense to you.

17:34.303 --> 17:36.180
They do make
sense. Just ask me!

17:36.347 --> 17:38.441
Okay, that's what
I'm doin'. All right?

17:38.516 --> 17:41.395
So now I'm gonna ask you,
from where you were standing,

17:41.477 --> 17:42.979
could you see
the traffic light?

17:44.605 --> 17:48.075
Could you tell me if it was red?
Yellow? Green?

17:48.150 --> 17:49.367
She just came
out of nowhere?

17:49.443 --> 17:50.990
What color
was the light?

17:51.529 --> 17:53.327
Boy, I'm sorry...

17:57.994 --> 17:59.541
I..

18:00.413 --> 18:02.165
I guess it was green?

18:02.290 --> 18:03.792
Green?

18:05.751 --> 18:07.503
I think it was
just an accident.

18:10.006 --> 18:11.474
Where were
you at?

18:11.591 --> 18:13.093
I was on Broadway.

18:25.438 --> 18:27.190
What happened to you?
Nothing.

18:29.692 --> 18:30.693
Hello?

20:07.456 --> 20:09.208
So, does anybody
know who she was?

20:09.625 --> 20:11.673
