she lived around here

20:11.794 --> 20:13.842
if she had all these
Fairway grocery bags.

20:14.088 --> 20:15.214
What did they do
with her leg?

20:15.297 --> 20:17.015
I have no fucking idea.
Hey...

20:21.971 --> 20:24.099
Lisa? Are you sure
you don't want me to call in?

20:24.181 --> 20:25.933
Oh, no, thanks.

20:26.016 --> 20:28.269
I mean, thank you.
That's really sweet.

20:28.394 --> 20:30.647
But I'm supposed to
go see Becky anyway,

20:30.730 --> 20:33.483
