I'll be all right.

20:50.750 --> 20:52.844
- Hey.
- Hey, Darren.

20:53.669 --> 20:54.716
Hey.

21:03.846 --> 21:05.564
Joan?
Yeah?

21:05.765 --> 21:06.982
