know me anymore.

21:21.197 --> 21:22.414
Hey, are you
comin' out?

21:22.531 --> 21:23.783
Um... I don't know.
I'm not sure.

21:23.866 --> 21:24.992
Come on.
Maybe I will.

21:25.075 --> 21:26.543
I don't know if I'm going to.
But I might.

21:26.827 --> 21:28.295
See you later.
Bye.

21:28.412 --> 21:29.709
- Goodnight.
- See you later.

21:30.831 --> 21:32.879
Hi, are you Ramon?

21:32.958 --> 21:37.213
Yes. Hello. You were
wonderful again.

21:37.296 --> 21:40.846
Oh, you're so sweet. And thank
you for the beautiful flowers.

21:40.925 --> 21:42.347
You're very welcome.

21:42.468 --> 21:43.845
And you've seen
the show before?

21:43.928 --> 21:45.475
Yes, two times.

21:45.554 --> 21:49.058
Gosh. That's a lot!

21:49.266 --> 21:51.485
It's a beautiful performance.

21:51.727 --> 21:53.650
I'm sure you will
have a big success.

21:53.729 --> 21:56.699
Well, right now, we're just trying
to focus on what we're doing.

21:57.358 --> 21:59.486
